latestPosts.caption:
Novas Nursery 💛

The most calming little room I just love it 🥰 although we used that changing mat for maybe 3 days and have now restored to puppy pads down on our bed during the middle of the night 😂 thanks @barbellbarbiex for that recommendation - life saving.

Swipe for a before of the room. I am so glad novas gran was part of the decoration in this room too. She helped me paint it without even being asked because that was just the type of woman she was 🥰 

These past few weeks have been rough but I’m so glad for all the support I’ve had from friends & family and everyone on here - thank you all ❤️

.
